    <p class="lead">Two different services for two different problems. When the problem is a damaged or failed component, call us. When the problem is lint-accumulation in a long vent run, call a cleaning specialist. When it could be either, our $89 diagnostic establishes which.</p>

    <div class="choose-grid">
